<taxonomicName authorityName="Melichar" authorityYear="1923" box="[542,700,937,961]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Makilingia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="intermedia">
<emphasis box="[542,700,937,961]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="487">M. intermedia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in coloration but differs in having the pale markings of the clavus more extensive and the processes of the aedeagal atrium greatly enlarged.
</paragraph>
